## 2. LoRA adapter weights (Research-only)

The LoRA adapter binary (`adapter_model.safetensors` and related files,
distributed via GitHub Releases) is released for **academic and research use
only**.

You are permitted to:
- Use the adapter in non-commercial research
- Fine-tune further for academic experiments
- Cite this work in publications

You are NOT permitted to:
- Use the adapter for commercial fanfic generation services
- Redistribute generated text as if it were original work
- Use generated content in any way that violates the copyrights of the
  underlying source novels

## 3. The underlying source data

The source novels (《吞噬星空》, 《吞噬星空 2 起源大陆》, 《雪鹰领主》)
and the 120 fan-written derivative works used to train this model are NOT
included in this repository and are NOT covered by this license.

- The original novels remain copyright 我吃西红柿 (I-Eat-Tomatoes) and Qidian.
- Fan-written derivative works remain copyright their respective authors.
- The worldview annotations in `tier_notes.md` (full version, not included)
  are research-only and constitute commentary/analysis, not reproduction.

Users of this code must obtain their own copies of source material and use
this software only in ways consistent with the applicable copyright laws of
their jurisdiction.

## 4. Generated outputs

Content generated by this system using the included code and a trained adapter
constitutes a derivative work of the source novels. Such generated content:

- Is the user's responsibility under copyright law
- May not be commercially distributed
- May be shared for non-commercial academic discussion with proper attribution

## 5. No warranty for canonicity

While the anti-hallucination Checker reduces factual errors, generated content
may still contain inaccuracies relative to the source canon. No warranty is
made regarding the accuracy of generated text.

